    "To address this challenge, it is essential to comprehend the motivations behind participation.",
    "Researchers agree that enjoyment is a crucial factor in driving participation (Lindenberg, 2001; Malone et al., 2010).",
    "A robust connection has been discovered between enjoyment and increased engagement in a crowdsourcing activity.",
    "Individuals who partake in enjoyable crowdsourcing activities are more likely to invest time and effort, resulting in more contributions and greater satisfaction with the final product (Frey et al., 2011; Liang et al., 2018).",
